LibreBSD is a network security operating system based on freebsd for UTM and firewall appliances. this project will release under BSD license which produced by Metaco Group Network Division. This product is fully open source and its interface is based on HTML5 and CSS3 and its backend is based on Python and Perl with FreeBSD/NanoBSD platform.

This product is under development and not work correctly so don't try it ! For contribution and more information contact Roozbeh Shafiee the project founder and core developer with RoozbehOnline@Gmail.Com and RoozbehShafiee.Com